      "content": "telehealth is so expensive and i just want a quick fix so i can get back to work... i have some old antibiotic eye drops from a previous prescription in my medicine cabinet. if i just use those for a day or two, won't that clear up whatever this is? it seems way more efficient than waiting for an appointment.",
